2. User Creation — Allow Public Role in POST Validation

---

Affected endpoint: `POST /api/admin/users`

Changes made:

* Expanded allowed roles:
  * From `['staff', 'admin']`
  * To `['public', 'staff', 'admin']`
* Updated validation error message to reflect all supported roles
* Ensured role lookup (`user_type` → `user_type_id`) supports `public`
* Normalized phone number input before validation and storage

Behavior breakdown:

| Scenario                  | Before                              | After                                      |
| ------------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| Creating public user      | Rejected (invalid user_type)        | Accepted                                   |
| Creating staff/admin user | Accepted                            | Unchanged                                  |
| Phone formatting input    | Could fail validation unexpectedly  | Normalized to digits before validation      |
| Invalid role input        | Error message incomplete            | Error message reflects all valid roles      |

